A well thought out capsule wardrobe, on the other hand, really works for us because it‚Äôs designed with intention. I tried to create one for years and was unsuccessful until I learned my best colors. There were a few places that, now looking back, I see I went wrong.
What doesn‚Äôt work for trying to create a capsule wardrobe‚Ä¶
