#2 ‚Äì I tried the ‚Äúneutral thing‚Äù ‚Äì At the end of the day, I‚Äôm just not a neutrals gal. Some women are, and genuinely love wearing black, grey, white, and beige all the time. I can not. I get sooooo bored. I don‚Äôt even have one single black and white picture in my house. So, while sure, I might choose a few capsule wardrobe basics in a few neutrals, I want to see lots of gorgeous, rich colors when I fling open my closet doors.
